# Keep Cargo.lock byte-identical across platforms. Windows runners default to
# core.autocrlf=true and would rewrite it to CRLF, which changes
# hashFiles('Cargo.lock') (diverging the Windows Rust cache key) and perturbs
# cargo's build fingerprints. Scoped to this one file on purpose — we do not
# want to force eol on Windows-native files.
Cargo.lock text eol=lf
